snippet.title: Scrabble Interactive: 2003 Edition - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
While Scrabble had two versions on the PSone (one in the US by Hasbro Interactive and one in Europe by Ubisoft), the 2003 Edition for the PlayStation 2 was released exclusively in Europe.

Scrabble (C) Mattel
Developed by Runecraft
Published by Ubisoft
